<br>
I have also begun a system. After I res (unless I am in a good mood) I wont heal you unless given a donation. That is a system I use genrally when I receive 20 tells in the first 5 minutes that I have logged on. I have no idea how I end up with roleplay off in areas like Kunark where res tells are abundant.<br>
<br>
